{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994950/extras/Lance.gif?t=1737812620\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to explore Throw Island as you, jump, slide, and most importantly, throw your way to victory. Throw Bro is a challenging, modern GameBoy-style, 2D platforming game where you use your enemies against them by throwing them at each other. As you play you will find many unique secrets and puzzles and ultimately find out who took Throw Gal! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994950/extras/Gameplay.png?t=1737812620\" />Have fun traversing through 35+ unique levels, each building on each other. There are 6 unique worlds in Throw Bro, each of them introducing unique mechanics that you can only take advantage of with your throw ability. There are additional bonus levels for players who take the time to gather all the collectables in each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994950/extras/Big_CIty.gif?t=1737812620\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994950/extras/Boss_Fights.png?t=1737812620\" />Prepare to hone your throwing skills to take down some tough opponents. Throw Bro has many boss fights, each one challenging your skills in different and unique ways. Get ready to dodge and throw to put an end to the evil-doers of Throw Island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994950/extras/Features.png?t=1737812620\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throwing items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dashing ability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sliding ability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speedrunning Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">35+ Levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bonus levels for those who collect all the collectables</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many hidden secrets in each world that you will have to discover for yourself</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We hope you can enjoy Throw Bro and the care that was put into the gameplay, story, art, and music. Get ready, and go throw!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Great Start!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2994950/d9b47917f2b127bcc13b8abcfba4cce3613ddaf8.jpg"},{"name":"B-b-b-Bonus Level!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2994950/4c24766d9cdfecb769e6495e3537e4415c258e4a.jpg"},{"name":"Professional Spelunker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2994950/340ce148cb360d41d65bd4e46200435a8877f43b.jpg"},{"name":"Sun Bathing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2994950/c3a427ba60e4d73f62eb01f492df49c79d9021a4.jpg"},{"name":"It's Too Hot!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2994950/ae32deaa58d8eaf59874e59c171417b579740b8c.jpg"},{"name":"City Lights","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2994950/26ab00a0c23b237dc1e1d7a17e6bfa87b5c110f4.jpg"},{"name":"The Biggest Bonus","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2994950/4edaa3ebce4b3657ee457a56d1111d4a9f3819c2.jpg"},{"name":"Who's this?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2994950/c76befa3bc884b7158c4a97dc435eacc8480c661.jpg"},{"name":"How's this?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2994950/ea488c3